name: LifeSpeak Inc
longDescription: LifeSpeak Inc is a software-as-a-service provider of a platform for mental health and total wellbeing education for organizational employees and customers. LifeSpeak's proprietary library's depth and breadth of easily consumable content helps companies around the world support their people anytime and anywhere. The firm serves a diverse global client base across many industries and sectors, including Fortune 500 companies, government agencies, insurance providers, and other health technology firms. The company derives revenue from subscription of its product (subscription revenue) comprised of its hosted platform. It generates most of the revenue from Canada.
